---
title: Salmon Limone over Herbed Couscous with Zucchini & Tomato
description: Limone is Italian for lemon, so you know this dish is going to have plenty of citrusy flavor. We start with tender, butter-toasted Israeli couscous, upgraded with juicy tomato, sautéed zucchini, and a double dose of lemon zest and juice. It’s all topped with pan-seared salmon dusted with our Italian seasoning. Drizzle with a lemony crema for the finishing touch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6798fd2635c238be91c9a770-969ffba6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6798fd2635c238be91c9a770-en-US.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
cuisine: Southern Europe
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/salmon-limone-6798fd2635c238be91c9a770
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
